import { RegisterService } from '../register.service'; import { User } from '../user'; import { Component, OnInit } from '@angular/core'; @Component({ selector: 'app-register-user', templateUrl: './register-user.component.html', styleUrls: ['./register-user.component.css'] }) export class RegisterUserComponent implements OnInit{ user:User=new User(); constructor(private registerService:RegisterService){ } ngOnInit():void{ } userRegister(){ console.log(this.user); this.registerService.registerUser(this.user).subscribe(data=> { alert("user registration is successful") }, error=>alert("sorry user is not registered")); } }
